Model Options:

Speed Mode: FP8E5M2 model + Enable quantization (faster, lower memory)
Quality Mode: FP8E4M3 model + Disable quantization (better quality, slower)

Note: Do not enable quantization with FP8E4M3 model as it may cause errors.

A cinematic sequence of a female Star Wars-style warrior standing on a crumbling tower at twilight. She wears battle-scarred futuristic armor with flowing dark robes, silhouetted against a stormy sky.
A cinematic scene, smooth transition. A man inside a subway car, as the camera retreats, he appears to stand alone in a vintage subway car that appears to be suspended in a misty, ethereal void.
a little monster is being touched
a cat next to a river

A close-up shot of a young woman standing against a graffiti-covered corridor wall. She wears a grey hoodie with a faded bear graphic, her hair tied in a messy bun. The camera slowly dolly zooms out as she raises her chin slightly and smiles with subtle confidence, eyes fixed on the lens. Warm bokeh lights blur behind her down the hallway, adding depth and intimacy. Her expression shifts from surprise to playful defiance, as if teasing the viewer with a secret. The mood is cinematic, cozy, and spontaneous  a slice of street-life charm.

Cinematic and epic scene. Realistic details. A gritty close-up of an elven kings face, his silver-blonde hair cascading in intricate braids, brows slightly arched as he gazes just off-camera with cold composure. The camera dollies out over his shoulder, revealing a majestic white stag standing silently in the forest behind him, its antlers dappled with morning mist. The moment holds stillness and unspoken authority. Lighting is dawnlight filtering through ancient trees, cool-toned and ethereal with soft highlights on moss and leaves.
A gazelle walked towards the woman. The woman looked back gently.

You might notice that our negative prompt uses Chinese. Through extensive testing, weve found that prompts written in Chinese consistently yield better image generation results, particularly when filtering out unwanted features.

To ensure full transparency, heres the English meaning of the Chinese terms used:
Over-saturated colors, overexposure, static composition, blurry details, subtitles, stylistic distortion, generic artwork, painting-like appearance, dull framing, stillness, overall gray tone, worst quality, low quality, JPEG compression artifacts, ugliness, incompleteness, extra fingers, poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn faces, deformities, disfigurement, deformed limbs, fused fingers, motionless frames, cluttered backgrounds, three legs, overcrowded background, walking backward.

This setup helps optimize the visual quality while keeping the prompt configuration as effective as possible. Thanks for understanding!

fp8_fast seems to cause huge quality degradation

fp_16_fast enables "Full FP16 Accmumulation in FP16 GEMMs" feature available in the very latest pytorch nightly, this is around 20% speed boost. 

Sageattn if you have it installed can be used for almost double inference speed
